ing: 1 sweet potato, cut into long thin slices, or more as needed
n: Sweet and Spicy Sweet Potato Baked Fries!
des: "This recipe came after visiting a restaurant and trying to duplicate it at home! It is easy, too. Serve with honey mustard."
ins:
Preheat oven to 400 degrees F (200 degrees C).
Mix olive oil, honey, cayenne pepper, and black pepper in a large bowl. Add sweet potato slices; toss to coat. Arrange coated sweet potatoes on a baking sheet.
Bake in the preheated oven until fries are slightly crisp, 30 to 40 minutes.
